{"type":null,"faqId":8845,"title":"荣耀X1（7D-501u）7.0  是否支持 microSD 卡升级？怎么操作？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>支持。</span></span> \n</p>\n<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29292\" /> \n<div style=\"margin-left:3cm;\">\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">系统升级会清除荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">上的所有数据。建议您先备份数据后再升级。</span></span> \n\t</p>\n\t<p>\n\t\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l<span>&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\"><span>使用非授权的软件升级时，可能会造成升级失败、个人信息泄露等风险。建议您使用在线升级或下载官方发布的版本进行升级。</span></span> \n\t</p>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">请先从正规渠道下载升级包，并将升级包中的</span><span>&nbsp;<b>dload</b>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">文件夹拷贝到</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡根目录下。然后在主屏幕上点击</span> <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29297\" /></span><b><span></span></b><span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">设置</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">常规设置</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">手机升级</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">系统软件更新</span></b><span> &gt; </span><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">本地升级</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">会自动检测</span><span> microSD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">卡里的升级包并进行升级。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=29296\" /></span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span></span></span>&nbsp;\n</p>\n&nbsp;\n<p>